# financial-metrics-model

## Core Financial Components

### Service Cost Calculations
- Mileage cost tracking with fixed rate of $0.67/mile
- Automated aggregation of travel costs per service type
- Service-specific billing code calculations for:
  - Travel services (PT, FS-OH, FS-IH)
  - Drug testing (5 distinct billing categories)
  - Case management services
  - Intake assessments

### Staff Performance Metrics
- Hour tracking across service categories
- Trip count aggregation by service type
- Mileage accumulation per staff member
- Service delivery efficiency measurements

### Hour Classification System
1. Billable Hours:
   - Face-to-face service time
   - Direct client interaction periods
   
2. Transport Hours:
   - PT service travel time
   - FS-OH transit periods
   - FS-IH travel segments

3. Indirect Hours:
   - FS-OH supporting activities
   - FS-IH documentation time
   - Non-client facing preparation

### Financial Reporting Engine
- Aggregated service metrics by category
- Staff performance summaries
- Cost center analysis by service type
- Mileage expense reporting

